Dear Rick, Do you need an apprentice? If you have never seen his shows I urge you to start now!
Rick has these video's and a set of guides for traveling. Listing and showing back street finds that are not crowded out by tourista's. It's definitely helping with our trip planning.
I have been to many of the same places and really enjoyed seeing how things have changed or not after all these years.

Love this one and watching it.  It is very clear and well done vs. some of the older ones i have just run across so I would advise any buyers to be aware that not all are the same even in the DVD's quality.
